{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ca36422d-e5f1-4c08-bcb6-7987b0c9c02d","content":"`.testsettings` files are **no longer supported** in modern MSTest (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's a breakdown of your settings and their equivalents:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| `AssemblyResolution` | No longer needed (handled by the SDK) |\n| Code Coverage `DataCollector` | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n\nLet me create the replacement:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_tEv0FMs9n1bzb4utzP7w9S","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_vWTBEFOmFvXAiIciHnExCn","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-1a826b571f5640f78b003b2a4e55d108/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileCodeCoverageDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-1a826b571f5640f78b003b2a4e55d108/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"16c0ae72-0ded-43b3-8c22-8d42567ffbb4","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file which is a legacy format. With MSTest v3+, the `.testsettings` file is no longer supported. They need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file.\n\nLet me anal